	<h1>Youth Advisory Board Positions are Available</h1>
		

<p>To serve on the Youth Advisory Board, candidates must be:</p>
<ul>
	<li>14 to 19 years old, up to 21 if on an IEP</li>
	<li>on an Individualized Education Program (IEP) for emotional and behavioral disorders or diagnosed with a mental disorder such as anxiety, Asperger syndrome, attention deficit hyperactivity disorder, bipolar disorder, depression, or Tourette syndrome</li>
	<li>able to attend monthly meetings at PACER offices in Minneapolis</li>
	<li>willing to participate in presentations, in-services and other events</li>
</ul>
